      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, im working on this satirical screenplay about how ridiculous hollywood is and i really dont want to accidentally fall into any old cliches. can u help me out? can u list like 5 common racial stereotypes that movies always use so i can make sure i'm either avoidin them or using them in a way that's actually ironic? thanks",
